{{wiktionary|Asia Minor}}
'''[[Asia Minor]]''' is an alternative name for Anatolia, the westernmost protrusion of Asia, comprising the majority of the Republic of Turkey.

'''Asia Minor''' may also refer to:
* [[Asia Minor (instrumental)|"Asia Minor" (instrumental)]], a 1961 instrumental recording by Jimmy Wisner (operating under the name Kokomo)
* [[Asia Minor (album)|''Asia Minor'' (album)]], an album by Jamaican-born jazz trumpeter Dizzy Reece
